Horoscopes

In the horoscopes I occasionally write for Yasmin Boland, I was telling everyone to be careful of acting impulsively (Mars in conjunct Jupiter). Standing unprotected in the middle of crazy weather defo qualifies for acting impulsively! Best to follow my own advice!
